---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Gnocchi and Chicken Breasts with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden, pan-fried gnocchi add a delicious twist to classic Alfredo topped with chicken! Rich cream and savoury Parmesan come together to make a luscious sauce for this supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/parmesan-pan-fried-gnocchi-abfb13cf-21eed790.jpg
